Class AppointmentOutcomeRecord

java.lang.Object
AppointmentOutcomeRecord
public class AppointmentOutcomeRecord extends Object
The `AppointmentOutcomeRecord` class manages the records of past appointments. It is implemented as a Singleton to ensure only one instance exists throughout the application. The class provides methods to add, retrieve, and display appointment outcomes.
